dataIdInfo.idPurp:
Vector200 - Administrative Boundary VECTOR200 is a 2D landscape model, which represents the natural and man-made features of the landscape in vector format. With its high generalisation grade (scale 1:200 000) it is a reference dataset for applications requiring a regional or national overview.
http://www.swisstopo.admin.ch/internet/swisstopo/de/home/products/landscape/vector200.html
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
The Topic Administrative Boundaries contains different administrative boundaries. In addition to the municipal, district, canton and national boundaries, the national parks in Switzerland and neighboring countries are also shown. The Topic consists of 3 feature classes und 2 tables.

http://www.swisstopo.admin.ch/internet/swisstopo/de/home/products/landscape/vector200.html
